node.text:
UPPER BOOTY 🍑
.
TAG a friend!
.
Eeeeek @nvgtn announcement coming very soooon 🙈😆👏🏼!! Stay tunedddd 👀
.
Ended the weekend with a pretty relaxed glute day 😌 I took it easy today and focused on some accessory movements, but more so just wanted to be active ✨ Honestly though, it turned out to be nice lil workout! 🥳
.
Give these movements a try on you next glute workout 💪🏼
.
1️⃣ Kneeling Overhead squat - 4x15
2️⃣ Banded squat variation - 3x20
3️⃣ Overhead reverse lunge - 4x10 each leg
4️⃣ Slow sumo squats - 4x20
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
Outfit- @nvgtn

FAT BURNER 🔥
.
TAG a friend!
.
Are you seeing, what I’m seeing 👀🙊🤎 @nvgtn
.
Eeeek something BIG is coming and I cannot WAIT for you to find out 🤩!
.
If you’re looking for a quick, killer cardio sesh, give this one a try! This can be done anywhere, anytime! 💪🏼 You can perform this as a circuit or just do each exercise and they’re sets, separately! Either way I promise you’ll feel the burn 🔥 🥵
.
1️⃣ Squat/oblique twist - 4x15
2️⃣ Side jump squat- 3x20
3️⃣ Side lunge/high knee - 4x15 each leg
4️⃣ Squat jump variation - 3x20
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
Outfit- @nvgtn

node.text:
5 Year Transformation ✨
.
TAG a friend!
.
The first video in each slide was roughly 6 months into the start of my fitness journey, where I was weighing about 90lbs with clothes on and living a super obsessive and restrictive lifestyle ⏩ fast forward to the second video in each slide, which is where I’m at currently, weighing about 115lbs and living a much more sustainable and happy lifestyle 👏🏼
.
I loved myself in the first phase but this version of me is where I’m happiest 🥰! It sounds cheesy but, I finally feel free! Free from all of the stress food used to cause me, free from the fear of the scale and free from an unfulfilling, restrictive lifestyle 😌
.
It’s great to have goals but it’s also important to not lose yourself in the process of achieving them! You’re perfect just the way you are 💓
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
.
Outfit- @nvgtn 
_____________________________

node.text:
BOOTY BURNER 🔥
.
TAG a friend!
.
Ending the weekend with a killer glute sesh 🥵 I wanted to finish my workout off with some accessory style movements to really burnout my muscles, and boy did I 😅 These may look 
simple, but I promise you, you will feel the burn 🔥
.
Give these a try on your next glute day! 👏🏼
.
1️⃣ Squat jump pulse - 4x10
2️⃣ Sumo Squat walks - 4x20 sec
3️⃣ Stagger stance lunge - 4x15 each leg
4️⃣ Side lunge slides - 4x20
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
Outfit- @nvgtn
_____________________________

THE @nvgtn LAUNCH IS NOW LIVE! 🤩
.
Head over to nvgtn.com to shop our 𝟮𝟰 fully restocked Contour Seamless Legging colors 🌈 AND our brand 𝙉𝙀𝙒 Scrunch Seamless Collection! 🥳👏🏼
.
I’m so so sooo excited for you guys to finally get your hands on these pieces!! I know you’re going to look amazing in all of it! 😍
.
If you choose to shop with us today, thank you all so incredibly much! It truly means the world to us! 🥺💓
.
With that being said, 𝗛𝗔𝗣𝗣𝗬 𝗟𝗔𝗨𝗡𝗖𝗛 𝗗𝗔𝗬!! 
.

SIDE BOOTY 🍑
.
TAG a friend!
.
Eeeeek tomorrow is the @nvgtn launch and I’m screaming with excitement 😆👏🏼👏🏼!! 
.
This is going to be our biggest Contour Seamless Legging restock EVER! We are fully restocking our Contour Leggings in 24 colors 😍 And this is the first release of our NEW Scrunch Seamless Collection 🔥🙌🏼 I cannot wait for you to get your hands on it all!!
.
If you’re looking for some killer movements to fire up your glute medius, give these a try! 💪🏼
.
1️⃣ Single leg thrust - 4x15 each side
2️⃣ Squat/side leg raise - 3x20 each leg
3️⃣ Alternating side lunge - 4x15
4️⃣ Fire hydrant variation - 3x15 each leg
.
@brettstir 🎥💕

node.text:
LOWER ABS 🔥
.
TAG a friend!
.
Oouufff this one had my belly burnin’ 🥵 Ended today’s lift with some outdoor abs ☀️ Trying to take advantage of the sunshine in between these rain storms ☔️ gotta love the rainy season 🥲
.
If you’re looking for a killer challenge, give these exercises a try! You can either do this as a circuit or individually! 💪🏼
.
1️⃣ Bird dog - 3x15 each side 
2️⃣ Star crunch - 3x10
3️⃣ Reverse plank crunch - 3x20
4️⃣ Frog extensions - 3x15
.
@brettstir 🎥💓
Outfit- @nvgtn ~ olive agility bra, black speckled scrunch shorts~
Dropping: July 17th, 10am est

node.text:
4 DAYS OUT FROM THE @nvgtn LAUNCH 😍
.
Wanted to switch things up this time around, so I decided to do a mini try on haul here! 🥳
.
This launch is primarily a contour legging restock, but we have added our NEW Scrunch Seamless Collection and I’m OBSESSED 👏🏼 I cannot wait for you guys to get your hands on these pieces!! 🔥
.
Let me know in the comments down below of any questions you have regarding the launch and I will do my best to answer them! 💓
.
Scrunch Leggings:
✨ Fuchsia
✨ Grey
✨ Black Speckled
. 
Scrunch Shorts:
✨ Fuchsia 
✨ Grey
✨ Black Speckled
.
Dropping July 17th, 10AM est ⏰
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
____________________________

node.text:
UNDER BOOTY 🍑
.
TAG a friend!
.
I hope everyone had a great start to their week! 🤗
.
When I was younger, I used to dreaddd Monday’s 😩 but now, I honestly love them! 😂 Weekends are very much needed but I love feeling productive and having that fresh start to the week feeling, knowing so much will be accomplished throughout the upcoming days 👏🏼 
.
Is it just me or does anyone else feel like this? 🙈😅
.
Anyways, here are a few of my favorites movements from today’s lift that you can incorporate into your next glute workout! 💪🏼
.
1️⃣ SDL variation - 4x10 each leg
2️⃣ Yoga ball thrusts - 4x20
3️⃣ Half lunge/kickback pulse - 3x20 each leg 
4️⃣ Seated good mornings - 3x15
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
Outfit- @nvgtn ~coral contour leggings, white axis bra~
Launching: July 17th 10am est 
_________________________
#fitfam #fitness #fitnessmotivation #fitnessjourney #fitlife #workout #workoutmotivation #glutes #glutesworkout #squats #squatbooty #healthylifestyle #happiness #positivevibes #summer #florida

node.text:
HOME ABS ✨
.
TAG a friend!
.
Duke would give up all of his doggy toys just to have one car toy, specifically a mouse 😂 but I don’t think the kitties are amused 🙈 lol
.
Did a little home ab workout today and wanted to share! This is perfect to do as an add on to your workout, or to do just to get your body moving if you’re stuck at home 🤗 You can do these as a circuit or individually! 💪🏼
.
1️⃣ Weighted leg raises - 3x15
2️⃣ Bridge hold/extension- 3x20
3️⃣ Oblique crunch variation - 3x20 each side 
4️⃣ Scissor variation - 3x30 sec
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
Outfit- @nvgtn

node.text:
SUMMER BURN 🔥 
.
TAG a friend!
.
If you’re looking for a killer sweat sesh, this one’s for you 👏🏼🥵 If you want a quick cardio workout, you can easily make this into a circuit that you can do anywhere, anytime! Or you can add this to finish off any workout for a full body burnout 💪🏼
.
1️⃣ Squat /oblique crunch - 4x20
2️⃣ Reverse lunge jump variation - 4x10 each leg
3️⃣ Jumping jack variation - 4x30 sec
4️⃣ Bicycle crunch variation - 4x15
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
Outfit- @nvgtn
